            <div type="transcript" id="J1213">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>We like March.</l>
                    <l>His Shoes are Purple --</l>
                    <l>He is new and high --</l>
                    <l>Makes he Mud for Dog and Peddler,</l>
                    <l>Makes he Forests dry.</l>
                    <l>Knows the Adder Tongue his coming</l>
                    <l>And presents her Spot --</l>
                    <l>Stands the Sun so close and mighty</l>
                    <l>That our Minds are hot.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>News is he of all the others --</l>
                    <l>Bold it were to die</l>
                    <l>With the Blue Birds exercising</l>
                    <l>On his British Sky.    version of 1872</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>We like March -- his shoes are Purple.</l>
                    <l>He is new and high --</l>
                    <l>Makes he Mud for Dog and Peddler --</l>
                    <l>Makes he Forests Dry --</l>
                    <l>Knows the Adders Tongue his coming</l>
                    <l>And begets her spot --</l>
                    <l>Stands the Sun so close and mighty --</l>
                    <l>That our Minds are hot.</l>
                    <l>News is he of all the others --</l>
                    <l>Bold it were to die</l>
                    <l>With the Blue Birds buccaneering</l>
                    <l>On his British sky --                                        version of 1878</l>
                </lg>

